== APPAREL ROW ==

= virtualenv =
virtualenv-2.6 --no-site-packages apparelrow

= buildout =
* Get the bootstrap.py script
  wget http://svn.zope.org/*checkout*/zc.buildout/trunk/bootstrap/bootstrap.py
* Run it (it will set up buildout)
  python bootstrap.py (if it complains about setuptools, easy_install setuptools)
* Run the buildout
  ./bin/buildout -v (fika...)
* Start the server
  ./bin/django-1.1.1 runserver

= Directory Structure =
.               This directory
./bin           General scripts, such as the FCGI daemon controller
./apparelrow    Django application root directory
./conf          Non-Django related configuration files, such as webserver config
./docs          General documentation


